{"word":"ὄντως","slug":"ὄντως","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ὄντως</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:participle'>part.</a> of <a href='S:εἰμί'><el>εἰμί</el></a> <i>(sum)</i>\n<p/><i>really, verily</i>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>; <el>ὄντως τε καὶ ἀληθῶς</el> <i>really</i> and truly, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/>"}]}